---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
---

<section class="relative pt-32 lg:pt-36">
  <Container className={"flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12"}>
    <div class="absolute w-full lg:w-1/2 inset-y-0 lg:right-0">
      <span
        class="absolute -left-6 md:left-4 top-24 lg:top-28 w-24 h-24 rotate-90 skew-x-12 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-60 lg:opacity-95 lg:block hidden"
      ></span>
      <span
        class="absolute right-4 bottom-12 w-24 h-24 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-80"
      ></span>
    </div>
    <span
      class="w-4/12 lg:w-2/12 aspect-square absolute -top-5 lg:left-0 rounded-full skew-y-12 blur-2xl opacity-40 skew-x-12 rotate-90"
    ></span>
    <div
      class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center lg:text-left lg:py-7 xl:py-8
        lg:items-start lg:max-w-none max-w-3xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:flex-1 lg:w-1/2"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-4xl/tight xl:text-4xl/tight font-bold text-heading-1"
      >
        Revolutionizing the <span
          class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600"
          >Digital Landscape</span
        > with Cutting-Edge Technology
      </h1>
      <Paragraph className="mt-8">
        At wohnmohr, we are at the forefront of innovation, transforming ideas
        into powerful digital solutions. Our passion for technology drives us to
        develop apps and software that are not only functional but also
        future-proof, setting new standards in the industry.
      </Paragraph>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-1 lg:w-1/2 lg:h-auto relative lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 mx-auto max-w-3xl"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/landing-image.webp"
        alt="Hero image"
        class="lg:absolute lg:w-full lg:h-full rounded-3xl object-cover lg:max-h-none max-h-96"
      />
    </div>
  </Container>

  <!-- <ByNumber /> -->
</section>
